{"tid":1367124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致一眾高官: 你出解放軍我最多返屋企，等你走左再上街，最受影響嘅係日日鬧示威者嗰班收成期，分清莊閒未?","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:09:04.000Z","uid":31215,"like":183,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"22f57dd58d1dfdf54fdec14d8429609c785c6734","tid":1367124,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"不知幾想你出<br />\n仲要唔止就咁出<br />\n最好搞到戒嚴<br />\n邊個出街拉邊個<br />\n旺角、金鐘、尖沙咀、銅鑼灣、上水、元朗，都泊幾架裝甲車坦克車，有士兵巡邏<br />\n<br />\n後生仔辛苦左咁耐終於可以放下暑假、打下機打下J<br />\n<br />\n等香港商家、地產，日日屌示威者阻住搵食嗰堆廢中廢老手停口停一排<br />\n諗起都開心<br />\n<br />\n咪睇下出解放軍可以出幾耐<br />\n出一年就有一年暑假放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45523bffc4d656f946b5809411d8d21e131f96d","tid":1367124,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491af49ae412d708dfcbbb21655f1366d9b3baa6","tid":1367124,"uid":140454,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"買定game係屋企煲<br />\n反正一路都餐餐公仔面根本無咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我反而搶心中產同有錢佬又無得出街食，賓妹又買唔到餸會餓死先"},{"pid":"fa2dfa5f76bfdde2184fb1021e5a2152639f2635","tid":1367124,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n《生於亂世，有種責任》<br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8dec30a048cd89d7a795315372913f52f04e0180","tid":1367124,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你靚仔咁撚串"},{"pid":"71e4bf13dbe9d04ac086668e43c54f021fffdd20","tid":1367124,"uid":164374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"求公投要求立即出解放軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e68296426141702071b8d784ba4ecc49e419edb","tid":1367124,"uid":266112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:21:02.000Z","msg":"Well, 人心是最難消滅的。<br />\n繼續打飛機話外國勢力介入，反對派煽動操控law"},{"pid":"3069986921da67cb5f1bd5377fc9d7462295a4ff","tid":1367124,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府入面嘅暴徒聽住 ！<br />\n<br />\n如果香港市民嘅遊行活動裡面，有任何示威者被襲擊受傷甚至死亡嘅話，而你地冇全力協助防御拯救 ！<br />\n<br />\n即係代表你地唔能夠代表人民去保護人民嘅生命財產 ！<br />\n<br />\n咁你地只配得被自己生產嘅卵玷污 !<br />\n<br />\n睇下你地仲有乜卵用！<br />\n<br />\n自己計下條數，你地將會承受<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10,872,000次玷污</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n註1：毅進制遊行人數<br />\n6.9 ~ 24萬人<br />\n6.16 ~ 33.8萬人<br />\n7.1 ~ 19萬人<br />\n7.21 ~ 13.8萬人<br />\n每人1打中國雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n註2： 實際玷污次數應該係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">48,120,000次或以上</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/152134_09e95d81f988b6f6343512173f8a84d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F152134_09e95d81f988b6f6343512173f8a84d2.gif&h=24b48572&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ed627b2925825debf273e66a74345819be81336","tid":1367124,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dec30a048cd89d7a795315372913f52f04e0180","tid":1367124,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你靚仔咁撚串"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"D on9 狗官<br />\n靠嚇，想大人都未分清楚形勢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/don